# ai-extra.list — Other AI services not (yet) given a dedicated group
# Target group: Proxy  (generic foreign; region-agnostic)
# Format: one rule per line, TYPE,value  (NO trailing policy).
#
# Rationale: the project caps strategy groups at <=10 (ARCH 7). Claude, ChatGPT,
# GitHub, Google earn dedicated groups; the long tail of AI vendors routes
# through the generic Proxy group. Promote any of these to its own group later
# by adding a group + moving its lines to a new list — no architectural change.
# See docs/adr/ADR-0004-select-only-ai.md
#
# Perplexity
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,perplexity.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pplx.ai
DOMAIN,pplx-res.cloudinary.com
# xAI / Grok
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,x.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,grok.com
# OpenRouter
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openrouter.ai
# Microsoft Copilot (Bing/Sydney)
DOMAIN,copilot.microsoft.com
DOMAIN,sydney.bing.com
# Future (add as needed): DeepSeek, Mistral, Cohere, Poe ...
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,mistral.ai
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,cohere.com
